00:26:02,035 --> 00:26:04,257
It'll be a miraculous experience.  Unbelievable.

418
00:26:04,257 --> 00:26:04,949
Densha,

419
00:26:05,035 --> 00:26:06,539
Give it everything you got!

420
00:26:14,884 --> 00:26:16,052
You've openned my eyes.

