00:26:16,402 --> 00:26:19,049
I'll make this lie a reality.

422
00:26:34,504 --> 00:26:38,072
We'll go Sunday as planned.

423
00:26:38,072 --> 00:26:40,321
I hope the weather will be good.

424
00:26:47,422 --> 00:26:48,382
Please,

425
00:26:48,382 --> 00:26:51,016
Teach me to surf in the next 3 days.

426
00:26:52,935 --> 00:26:54,290
Please.

427
00:26:55,127 --> 00:26:55,814
In 3 days...

428
00:26:55,814 --> 00:26:57,831
what about work?

429
00:26:58,216 --> 00:27:01,089
