00:29:22,138 --> 00:29:23,629
Where's what?

458
00:29:23,642 --> 00:29:25,451
I'll tell you when I find one.

459
00:29:30,810 --> 00:29:33,210
How was it when you got back to Japan?

460
00:29:33,210 --> 00:29:35,002
How was it?

461
00:29:35,772 --> 00:29:38,118
